{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Village Heroes is a retro pixelart MMORPG. Embark on an adventure, team up with friends, explore a vast fantasy world, challenge powerful bosses, and collect rare treasures. Cultivate your own hero, craft legendary gear, conquer the Tower of Trials, and write your heroic legend!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2003640/extras/Hero_Commander.gif?t=1732150809\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Core Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Group Boss Battles</strong>\uff1aTeam up with friends to challenge powerful world bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hero Cultivation</strong>\uff1aCustomize your hero through talent trees, rune embedding, and elemental awakening.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Equipment Workshop</strong>\uff1aCraft unique artifacts through reinforcement, decomposition, and fusion.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hero Tower</strong>\uff1aChallenge the Hero Tower to unlock new heroes and earn hero fragments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Trial Tower</strong>\uff1aFace higher-level bosses, earn gold, and climb the ranks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Other Features</strong>\uff1aFree trading, battle pets, personalized outfits, random dungeon exploration.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2003640/extras/Hero_Druid.gif?t=1732150809\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Developer's Greeting</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Village Heroes is independently developed. There are still some shortcomings. I sincerely ask for your understanding and valuable suggestions. I will continue to optimize the game and strive for long-term operation. Thank you for your support!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.s